{"tid":563573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東頭邨病婦墮樓晾衫架保命　半天吊大嗌求助","createTime":"2018-02-17T05:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T05:28:56.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d591b0a818406d026767cbc1d587d4806452f0f7","tid":563573,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"黃大仙東頭邨彩東樓一名82歲姓羅老婦，昨晚近11時，被發現從高處飛墮而下，剛巧跌落11樓外牆晾衫架上，羅婦大難不死，即時大呼救命，一名84歲男街坊發現協助報警。消防接報趕至現場，爬出外牆將羅婦救回安全位置，她有骨折受傷，由救護車送院治理。警員調查後，相信羅婦因病厭世，事件無可疑。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180217/mobile/bkn-20180217010012778-0217_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180217%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180217010012778-0217_00822_001.html&d=vLdnCV632pcxTrTm5ZegE7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f5127a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180217/mobile/bkn-20180217010012778-0217_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da20e2f06ab5491a419270097be80a579a2a3071","tid":563573,"uid":3037,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"自殺不遂 死到一半後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}